metadata.name: Persuasive
metadata.description:
Falling into the deep end
Am I still awake?
Feels like I'm drowning
Am I Going insane? 

This is so overwhelming
Don't know how to calm down 
I'm going Crazy 
I'm falling down

What is this Bright Light?
That's Calling me out
It feels familiar 
I need to find out

Hey "Take a deep breath"
Its all gonna slow down
The Loop starts to break
Your Thoughts will calm down

Rusting Flow of thoughts
Will start to take a shape
Don't pull me down 
I'm not insane
I'm not drowning 
Just stuck in the lost train 
I'm rising above
Thank you for being there
